;&gt;&quot;`   :   value is &gt; magnitude \n* `&quot;&lt;=&quot;` : value is &lt;= magnitude \n* `&quot;&gt;=&quot;` : value is &gt;= magnitude \n* `&quot;~&quot;`   :   value is approximately magnitude \n\nIf not present, assumed meaning is  `&quot;=&quot;` . \n\">magnitude_status</a>, <a href=\"StructureDefinition-DV-QUANTIFIED.html\" title=\"Accuracy of measurement. Exact form of expression determined in descendants.\">accuracy</a>, <a href=\"StructureDefinition-DV-ABSOLUTE-QUANTITY.html\">accuracy</a>, <a href=\"StructureDefinition-DV-TEMPORAL.html\" title=\"Time accuracy, expressed as a duration.\">accuracy</a><br class=\"constraint\"/><span title=\"null\" class=\"constraint\">Constraints: </span><span style=\"font-weight:bold\" title=\"Value valid\" class=\"constraint\">Value_valid</span><br/></td></tr>\r\n<tr style=\"border: 0px #F0F0F0 solid; padding:0px; vertical-align: top; background-color: #F7F7F7\"><td style=\"vertical-align: top; text-align : var(--ig-left,left); background-color: #F7F7F7; border: 0px #F0F0F0 solid; padding:0px 4px 0px 4px; white-space: nowrap; background-image: url(tbl_bck00.png)\" class=\"hierarchy\"><img src=\"tbl_spacer.png\" alt=\".\" style=\"background-color: inherit\" class=\"hierarchy\"/><img src=\"tbl_vjoin_end.png\" alt=\".\" style=\"background-color: inherit\" class=\"hierarchy\"/><img src=\"icon_primitive.png\" alt=\".\" style=\"background-color: #F7F7F7; background-color: inherit\" title=\"Primitive Data Type\" class=\"hierarchy\"/> <a href=\"StructureDefinition-DV-DATE-TIME-definitions.html#DV_DATE_TIME.value\" title=\"ISO8601 date/time string.\">value</a><a name=\"DV_DATE_TIME.value\"> </a></td><td style=\"vertical-align: top; text-align : var(--ig-left,left); background-color: #F7F7F7; border: 0px #F0F0F0 solid; padding:0px 4px 0px 4px\" class=\"hierarchy\"/><td style=\"vertical-align: top; text-align : var(--ig-left,left); background-color: #F7F7F7; border: 0px #F0F0F0 solid; padding:0px 4px 0px 4px\" class=\"hierarch